// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1049 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: f42adbb2-fb44-5a15-bc11-860f1201eea1

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
